messages.title: As your Labour MP I will:
messages.content: Save our NHS, with 20000 more nurses and 8000 more GPs. Change the law to stop letting agents charging rip-off fees. Expand free childcare for working parents. Action on zero hours contracts. Freeze energy bills until 2017. Make the UK's energy supply carbon zero by 2030.

leaflet.personalStatement: I know you feel betrayed by the Cambridge LibDem MP. The LibDems share the blame for NHS privatisation, a tax break for millionaires & tuition fees. I know what I stand for. I won’t let you down.
